---
// Problem V8 — Pourquoi les projets IA échouent (3 erreurs, pas un constat)
---

<section class="py-24" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Gauche : 3 erreurs -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 reveal" style="color: #f87171;">Pourquoi ça échoue ?</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6 reveal">
          Les 3 erreurs qui font
          <span class="font-serif italic" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);"> perdre du temps et de l'argent.</span>
        </h2>


        <div class="space-y-5">

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-1" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold" style="background: rgba(248,113,113,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.25); color: #f87171;">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Acheter des outils avant d'avoir identifié le problème</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">ChatGPT, Make, HubSpot, Notion... Chaque outil coûte entre 30 et 100 € par mois. Sans diagnostic préalable, vous payez pour des solutions à des problèmes que vous n'avez pas encore définis.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-2" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold" style="background: rgba(251,191,36,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.25); color: #fbbf24;">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Automatiser un processus qui n'est pas maîtrisé</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">L'IA n'améliore pas un processus cassé — elle l'accélère. Automatiser sans avoir d'abord structuré, c'est produire du chaos plus vite. Et perdre des mois de travail sur un projet que personne n'adopte.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-3" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold" style="background: rgba(129,140,248,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(129,140,248,0.25); color: #818cf8;">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Multiplier les expérimentations sans indicateurs de succès</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Tester 5 outils en parallèle, lancer 3 projets IA sans KPIs, changer de direction chaque mois. Sans boussole, impossible de savoir ce qui fonctionne — et impossible de défendre le budget engagé.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Droite : logos flottants + stat -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-right">
        <div class="logos-chaos relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 1/1; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 30%, rgba(248,113,113,0.06), transparent 50%), linear-gradient(135deg, #080d1a, #0a1020); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 right-0 text-center pointer-events-none" style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); text-transform: uppercase;">Vos outils · sans stratégie</div>

          <div class="logo-item" style="top:7%;  left:10%; animation-delay:0s;    --glow:rgba(16,185,129,0.45);"><img src="/icons/chatgpt.svg"   class="logo-svg" alt="ChatGPT"   width="42" height="42"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:5%;  left:50%; animation-delay:0.8s;  --glow:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"><img src="/icons/notion.svg"    class="logo-svg" alt="Notion"     width="36" height="36"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:4%;  right:8%; animation-delay:1.6s;  --glow:rgba(255,74,0,0.5);  "><img src="/icons/zapier.svg"    class="logo-svg" alt="Zapier"     width="40" height="40"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:28%; left:4%;  animation-delay:2.2s;  --glow:rgba(96,165,250,0.4);"><img src="/icons/anthropic.svg" class="logo-svg" alt="Claude"     width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:26%; left:36%; animation-delay:0.4s;  --glow:rgba(155,89,182,0.5);"><img src="/icons/make.svg"      class="logo-svg" alt="Make"       width="38" height="38"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:24%; right:6%; animation-delay:1.2s;  --glow:rgba(0,196,204,0.4); "><img src="/icons/canva.svg"     class="logo-svg" alt="Canva"      width="36" height="36"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:52%; left:16%; animation-delay:1.8s;  --glow:rgba(239,83,80,0.4); "><img src="/icons/n8n.svg"       class="logo-svg" alt="n8n"        width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:54%; left:50%; animation-delay:0.6s;  --glow:rgba(66,133,244,0.5);"><img src="/icons/gemini.svg"    class="logo-svg" alt="Gemini"     width="38" height="38"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:50%; right:5%; animation-delay:2.5s;  --glow:rgba(255,122,89,0.4);"><img src="/icons/hubspot.svg"   class="logo-svg" alt="HubSpot"    width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:74%; left:6%;  animation-delay:1.4s;  --glow:rgba(24,191,255,0.3);"><img src="/icons/airtable.svg"  class="logo-svg" alt="Airtable"   width="32" height="32"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:76%; left:42%; animation-delay:0.2s;  --glow:rgba(231,29,54,0.4); "><img src="/icons/slack.svg"     class="logo-svg" alt="Slack"      width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:72%; right:8%; animation-delay:2.0s;  --glow:rgba(251,191,36,0.35);"><img src="/icons/perplexity.svg" class="logo-svg" alt="Perplexity" width="32" height="32"/></div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Stat pleine largeur -->
    <div class="mt-10 p-7 rounded-2xl reveal" style="background: rgba(96,165,250,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.18);">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <div class="text-xs font-mono font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-2" style="color: var(--accent);">Le saviez-vous ?</div>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
            <span style="color: var(--accent);">58%</span> des dirigeants de PME n'ont aucune stratégie IA en place.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.francenum.gouv.fr/magazine-du-numerique/lia-dans-les-pme-et-eti-francaises-une-revolution-tranquille"
          target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs hover:opacity-70 transition underline underline-offset-2 flex-shrink-0"
          style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
          Bpifrance Le Lab · 1 200 dirigeants · 2025 ↗
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .logo-item {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    animation: logo-float 7s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 22px -6px var(--glow, rgba(96,165,250,0.3));
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .logo-item:hover {
    transform: scale(1.15) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 32px -4px var(--glow, rgba(96,165,250,0.5));
    z-index: 10;
  }
  .logo-svg {
    display: block;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(1);
    opacity: 0.85;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .logo-item:hover .logo-svg { opacity: 1; }
  @keyframes logo-float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
    25%       { transform: translateY(-9px) rotate(2deg); }
    75%       { transform: translateY(6px) rotate(-2deg); }
  }
</style>
